<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-6">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-4">What is SearchApp?</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
    SearchApp is a real-time search tracker that captures what users are typing as they search.
    The goal isn’t to perform the search itself, but to collect analytics on what users are interested in.
  </p>

  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
    <li>Tracks meaningful search phrases submitted by users.</li>
    <li>Displays analytics and trending searches over time.</li>
    <li>Helps understand what users are searching for the most.</li>
    <li>All searches are tracked anonymously using the user’s IP address only.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
